-30T04:16:59Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2025-07-30T04:16:59Z\",\"author_association\":\"OWNER\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/comments/3134800438\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/365#issuecomment-3134800438\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/365\"},{\"id\":3134800655,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOOm3QQc662UMP\",\"body\":\"**Claude finished @kesslerio's task** \u2014\u2014 [View job](https://github.com/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/actions/runs/16613328252)\\n\\n---\\n### Todo List:\\n- [x] Examine PR #358 to understand what it implemented\\n- [x] Check current state of notes formatter files mentioned in issue #365\\n- [x] Compare PR #358 changes with the issue #365 problem\\n- [x] Determine if issue needs updating, is resolved, or remains valid\\n- [x] Provide recommendation and analysis\\n\\n### Analysis: Issue #365 Status After PR #358\\n\\n#### **The Issue Remains Valid and Unresolved** \u26a0\ufe0f\\n\\nAfter examining the current codebase, I can confirm that:\\n\\n**PR #358 did NOT fix the core content extraction issue**. Here's what I found:\\n\\n#### Current State Analysis\\n\\n**1. Company Notes Formatter** (`src/handlers/tool-configs/companies/notes.ts:32`)\\n- \u2705 **Added**: Extensive debug logging (likely from PR #358)\\n- \u274c **Still Broken**: Only checks `note.content || ''` \\n- \u274c **Missing**: Multi-field content extraction\\n\\n**2. Person Notes Formatter** (`src/handlers/tool-configs/people/notes.ts:25`)\\n- \u274c **Still Broken**: Only checks `note.content`\\n- \u274c **Missing**: Debug logging entirely\\n- \u274c **Missing**: Multi-field content extraction\\n\\n**3. Test File Shows Correct Implementation** (`test/handlers/tool-configs/companies/notes.test.ts:19-24`)\\n- \u2705 **Has**: Complete multi-field extraction logic:\\n```typescript\\nconst content =\\n  note.content ||\\n  note.data?.content ||\\n  note.values?.content ||\\n  note.text ||\\n  note.body;\\n```\\n\\n#### What PR #358 Appears to Have Done\\n\\nBased on the current state, PR #358 likely added:\\n- Debug logging to company notes formatter (lines 20-26, 36-46)\\n- The comprehensive test suite for the content extraction issue\\n\\n**But it did NOT implement the actual fix in the production formatters.**\\n\\n#### Issue #365 Needs No Updates\\n\\nThe original issue description remains **100% accurate**:\\n- \u2705 Root cause analysis is correct\\n- \u2705 Proposed solution matches test implementation  \\n- \u2705 Both formatters still affected\\n- \u2705 Impact assessment still valid\\n\\n#### Recommendation\\n\\n**No updates needed to issue #365**. The issue should remain open and can be implemented as originally described. The test infrastructure is already in place, making implementation straightforward.\\n\\nThe real question is: Why wasn't the fix implemented when the tests were written? This suggests the work was partially completed but not finished.\\n\\n---\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"claude[bot]\",\"id\":209825114,\"node_id\":\"BOT_kgDODIGtWg\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/in/1236702?v=4\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/apps/claude\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"type\":\"Bot\",\"site_admin\":false,\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/events{/privacy}\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/following{/other_user}\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/followers\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/gists{/gist_id}\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/orgs\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/received_events\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/repos\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/subscriptions\"},\"reactions\":{\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0,\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/comments/3134800655/reactions\"},\"created_at\":\"2025-07-30T04:17:10Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2025-07-30T04:18:48Z\",\"author_association\":\"NONE\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/comments/3134800655\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/365#issuecomment-3134800655\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/365\"},{\"id\":3157438224,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOOm3QQc68Mq8Q\",\"body\":\"@claude based on new universal tool structure do we still need to fix this issue?\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"kesslerio\",\"id\":2647990,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjI2NDc5OTA=\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2647990?v=4\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/kesslerio\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"type\":\"User\",\"site_admin\":false,\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/events{/privacy}\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/following{/other_user}\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/followers\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/gists{/gist_id}\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/orgs\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/received_events\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/repos\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/subscriptions\"},\"reactions\":{\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0,\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/comments/3157438224/reactions\"},\"created_at\":\"2025-08-06T05:18:50Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2025-08-06T05:18:50Z\",\"author_association\":\"OWNER\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/comments/3157438224\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/365#issuecomment-3157438224\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/365\"},{\"id\":3157438519,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOOm3QQc68MrA3\",\"body\":\"**Claude finished @kesslerio's task** \u2014\u2014 [View job](https://github.com/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/actions/runs/16768224607)\\n\\n---\\n### Analysis: Issue #365 Status with Universal Tool Structure \\n\\n#### Todo List:\\n- [x] Examine current codebase structure and universal tool implementation\\n- [x] Check if note content extraction has been updated\\n- [x] Review original issue symptoms and root cause\\n- [x] Analyze if universal tools solve the content field mismatch problem\\n- [x] Provide clear recommendation on issue status\\n\\n### **Critical Finding: Issue #365 IS NOW OBSOLETE**\\n\\n#### **Root Cause Analysis**\\n\\nThe universal tool system has **fundamentally changed** how tools work:\\n\\n**1. Universal Tools Are Active By Default** \\n- `USE_UNIVERSAL_TOOLS_ONLY = true` (unless `DISABLE_UNIVERSAL_TOOLS=true`)\\n- Legacy resource-specific tools are **disabled** by default\\n\\n**2. Notes Tools Don't Exist in Universal System**\\n- \u274c `get-company-notes` - **NOT available** in universal tools\\n- \u274c `get-person-notes` - **NOT available** in universal tools  \\n- \u274c `create-company-note` - **NOT available** in universal tools\\n- \u274c `create-person-note` - **NOT available** in universal tools\\n\\n**3. Universal Tools Only Have Notes *Search*, Not Notes *Retrieval***\\n- \u2705 `search-by-content` with `content_type: \\\"notes\\\"` - searches BY notes content\\n- \u274c No tool to actually GET/DISPLAY note content\\n\\n#### **Current Universal Tool Coverage**\\n\\n**Core Operations (8 tools):**\\n- `search-records`, `get-record-details`, `create-record`, `update-record`, `delete-record`\\n- `get-attributes`, `discover-attributes`, `get-detailed-info`\\n\\n**Advanced Operations (5 tools):**\\n- `advanced-search`, `search-by-relationship`, `search-by-content`, `search-by-timeframe`, `batch-operations`\\n\\n**Missing Functionality:**\\n- **Notes retrieval/display** (`get-company-notes`, `get-person-notes`)\\n- **Notes creation** (`create-company-note`, `create-person-note`)\\n\\n#### **Issue Status: INVALID DUE TO ARCHITECTURE CHANGE**\\n\\n**The original issue #365 is no longer relevant because:**\\n\\n1. **The problematic tools don't exist anymore** - `get-company-notes` is not available when universal tools are active\\n2. **Users can't encounter the \\\"No content\\\" bug** - because the tool that causes it isn't exposed\\n3. **The field structure mismatch issue is bypassed** - since there's no tool to display note content\\n\\n#### **New Issue Required**\\n\\nThe real issue is now: **\\\"Universal tools missing notes management functionality\\\"**\\n\\n**Missing capabilities:**\\n- Cannot retrieve and display company/person notes\\n- Cannot create new notes for companies/people  \\n- Only can search records BY notes content, but can't see the notes themselves\\n\\n#### **Recommendation**\\n\\n**Close issue #365** as obsolete due to architecture change.\\n\\n**Create new issue:** \\\"Add notes management to universal tools\\\" with:\\n- `get-notes` universal tool (replace get-company-notes, get-person-notes)\\n- `create-note` universal tool (replace create-company-note, create-person-note) \\n- Proper content field handling (implementing the fix from original issue #365)\\n\\n---\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"claude[bot]\",\"id\":209825114,\"node_id\":\"BOT_kgDODIGtWg\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/in/1236702?v=4\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/apps/claude\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"type\":\"Bot\",\"site_admin\":false,\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/events{/privacy}\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/following{/other_user}\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/followers\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/gists{/gist_id}\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/orgs\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/received_events\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/repos\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/claude%5Bbot%5D/subscriptions\"},\"reactions\":{\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0,\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/comments/3157438519/reactions\"},\"created_at\":\"2025-08-06T05:19:00Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2025-08-06T05:20:59Z\",\"author_association\":\"NONE\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/comments/3157438519\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/365#issuecomment-3157438519\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/365\"},{\"id\":3157453813,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOOm3QQc68Muv1\",\"body\":\"# Triage Record - Post E2E Test Suite Analysis\\n\\n## Issue Review Summary (30 Open Issues Total)\\n\\nFollowing completion of the E2E test suite Sprint 1 (PR #374), I've conducted a comprehensive review of all open issues to provide prioritized recommendations for the next sprint.\\n\\n### Priority Distribution:\\n- **Priority High**: 1 issue\\n- **P1 (High)**: 3 issues  \\n- **P2 (Medium)**: 2 issues\\n- **P3 (Low)**: 17+ issues\\n- **Blocked**: 17 issues\\n\\n### Key Findings:\\n\\n#### 1. Critical Bug Ready for Immediate Action\\n**Issue #365 (This Issue)** - Notes content field mismatch\\n- **Status**: `priority:high`, `status:ready`, actively discussed\\n- **Impact**: Users cannot see note content in production\\n- **Effort**: Low (formatter update)\\n- **Recommendation**: Address immediately as next sprint priority\\n\\n#### 2. Post-Universal Tools Rollout Strategy Needed  \\n**Issue #364** - Universal tools rollout strategy (P1)\\n- **Context**: Universal tools implemented but need production rollout plan\\n- **Dependency**: Should follow #365 fix to avoid multiple deployments\\n\\n#### 3. Documentation Debt\\n**Issues #137, #67** - Both P1 documentation improvements\\n- **Impact**: Developer experience and adoption\\n- **Timing**: Can be parallelized with bug fixes\\n\\n#### 4. Testing Infrastructure Gaps\\n**Multiple issues** (#111, #114, #116, #117, #118) - All blocked, part of TDD milestone\\n- **Status**: 17 issues marked as `status:blocked`\\n- **Assessment**: Many blocked issues appear to be artificially blocked and could be unblocked\\n\\n## Immediate Recommendations for Next Sprint\\n\\n### Week 1-2: Critical Bug Fix \\u0026 Rollout\\n1. **Fix #365** - Notes content field structure (2-3 days)\\n2. **Implement #364** - Universal tools rollout strategy (1 week)\\n\\n### Week 3-4: Documentation \\u0026 User Experience  \\n3. **Address #137** - Documentation restructuring\\n4. **Work on #67** - API usage documentation with examples\\n\\n### Strategic Recommendations\\n\\n#### Issue Consolidation Opportunities\\n- **Deals Integration**: Issues #54, #55, #351 all relate to Deals API\\n  - **#351** provides strategic analysis and simplified implementation approach\\n  - Recommend prioritizing #351 over the older issues\\n\\n#### Blocked Issues Assessment\\n- **Many testing issues artificially blocked**: Issues #111, #114, #116, #117, #118\\n- **Recommendation**: Review blocking rationale, many could be unblocked and worked on\\n\\n#### Priority Adjustments Needed\\n- **Issue #351** (Deals Integration) - Well-researched strategic issue, consider upgrading from P2\\n- **Testing issues** - Multiple P3 testing issues could be consolidated under #111\\n\\n### Dependencies and Sequencing\\n1. **#365** \u2192 **#364** (Universal tools rollout after bug fix)\\n2. **#364** \u2192 **#351** (Deals integration after universal tools stable)\\n3. **#137** + **#67** can run parallel to technical work\\n\\n### Success Metrics for Next Sprint\\n- [ ] Notes content visible in production (#365)\\n- [ ] Universal tools rolled out with monitoring (#364)\\n- [ ] Documentation structure improved (#137)\\n- [ ] Blocked issues reviewed and unblocked where appropriate\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Next Action**: Prioritize Issue #365 for immediate implementation, followed by universal tools rollout strategy (#364).\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"kesslerio\",\"id\":2647990,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjI2NDc5OTA=\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2647990?v=4\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/kesslerio\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"type\":\"User\",\"site_admin\":false,\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/events{/privacy}\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/following{/other_user}\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/followers\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/gists{/gist_id}\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/orgs\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/received_events\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/repos\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kesslerio/subscriptions\"},\"reactions\":{\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0,\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/comments/3157453813/reactions\"},\"created_at\":\"2025-08-06T05:27:39Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2025-08-06T05:27:39Z\",\"author_association\":\"OWNER\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/comments/3157453813\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/365#issuecomment-3157453813\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/kesslerio/attio-mcp-server/issues/365\"}]"
